name: SPREAD THE DATA
description: This piece is a tribute to THE WATCHER, an ambitious, blockchain-based alternate reality game (ARG) in which the community tries to help the protagonist find their way home as they are lost in space. In the spirit of "spreading the data" to help THE WATCHER, this piece was created for the #OBJKT4OBJKT weekend. You can help by following THE WATCHER and joining us on the community discord server. *https://twitter.com/missingwatcher *Code-generated, 600x600, 18 seconds
